291
00:13:55,946 --> 00:13:56,346
Wait.

292
00:13:56,665 --> 00:13:57,745
Aren't you going to talk to her?

293
00:13:58,025 --> 00:13:59,505
Jiaren, wait...

294
00:14:01,706 --> 00:14:03,505
Jingjing. Your mom... You...

295
00:14:03,505 --> 00:14:04,346
Dad.

296
00:14:06,306 --> 00:14:07,025
Sorry.

297
00:14:07,586 --> 00:14:08,505
It was my fault.

298
00:14:08,586 --> 00:14:09,265
