that you would teach me how to drink

306
00:14:30,145 --> 00:14:31,066
when I come of age.

307
00:14:31,865 --> 00:14:32,426
I remember that.

308
00:14:32,986 --> 00:14:34,625
Learn how to drink while you're with me.

309
00:14:35,106 --> 00:14:36,145
