317
00:14:53,106 --> 00:14:54,145
Jingjing,

318
00:14:54,226 --> 00:14:55,745
you've inherited all my strengths,

319
00:14:56,025 --> 00:14:57,466
except

320
00:14:57,665 --> 00:14:58,385
my humor.

321
00:14:58,586 --> 00:14:59,986
I was just kidding.

322
00:15:01,706 --> 00:15:02,025
Cheers.

323
00:15:02,066 --> 00:15:02,665
Cheers.

324
00:15:11,625 --> 00:15:12,226
Jingjing.

325
00:15:13,586 --> 00:15:14,625
Please don't stay mad at me.

326
00:15:16,586 --> 00:15:17,826
