327
00:15:18,066 --> 00:15:18,745
if you compare me

328
00:15:18,946 --> 00:15:20,346
to other fathers.

329
00:15:20,946 --> 00:15:21,785
But I really want

330
00:15:21,946 --> 00:15:22,665
to do my best to protect you.

331
00:15:22,745 --> 00:15:23,665
