332
00:15:23,826 --> 00:15:24,865
even if it's just a little bit.

333
00:15:28,745 --> 00:15:29,946
In fact, I always know that.

334
00:15:31,066 --> 00:15:32,826
But there's just something
I still don't get.

335
00:15:33,426 --> 00:15:34,346
Since I was a kid,

336
00:15:34,505 --> 00:15:35,905
you've always believed in me

337
00:15:36,306 --> 00:15:37,265
and been supportive of everything I do.

338
00:15:38,226 --> 00:15:40,066
You believed that I would defeat

339
00:15:40,226 --> 00:15:41,826
the boy who practiced Taekwondo with me.

340
00:15:42,265 --> 00:15:43,346
You believed

341
00:15:43,545 --> 00:15:44,625
that I would do better in the next exam.

342
00:15:45,106 --> 00:15:46,426
You believed
that I wasn't a stupid student.

343
00:15:46,586 --> 00:15:47,106
That's right.

344
00:15:47,346 --> 00:15:47,826
You made me feel

345
00:15:47,946 --> 00:15:49,025
as if I was invincible.

346
00:15:49,505 --> 00:15:50,545
But somehow,

347
00:15:50,625 --> 00:15:52,986
you think I won't be able
to do it this time.

348
00:15:54,186 --> 00:15:55,106
Silly girl.

349
00:15:55,946 --> 00:15:57,066
Why would I doubt your capability?

350
00:15:57,145 --> 00:15:58,025
Why would I

351
00:15:58,066 --> 00:15:59,826
doubt my own daughter?

352
