358
00:16:13,025 --> 00:16:13,865
All I wanted to do

359
00:16:13,946 --> 00:16:15,505
was to spend every minute training.

360
00:16:15,745 --> 00:16:17,466
My dream was to join
the provincial team,

361
00:16:17,505 --> 00:16:19,106
then take part in the National Games
and win the championship.

362
00:16:20,745 --> 00:16:21,826
I even dreamed about
joining the national team

363
00:16:21,905 --> 00:16:23,265
and taking part in Olympics.

364
00:16:24,186 --> 00:16:25,426
Those were my dreams.

365
00:16:31,226 --> 00:16:32,905
But before the tryouts

366
00:16:32,986 --> 00:16:33,785
for the provincial team,

367
00:16:35,505 --> 00:16:36,665
I injured myself

368
00:16:36,826 --> 00:16:37,865
because I was working too hard

369
00:16:40,665 --> 00:16:41,265
on my training.

370
00:16:43,306 --> 00:16:44,186
You injured yourself?

371
00:16:45,545 --> 00:16:47,346
