377
00:17:00,226 --> 00:17:01,346
There were so many worries,

378
00:17:01,586 --> 00:17:02,505
even the unnecessary ones.

379
00:17:04,265 --> 00:17:05,386
I had no choice but to retire.

380
00:17:11,265 --> 00:17:12,706
Then, I met your mom.

381
00:17:14,065 --> 00:17:16,866
