to get into any university.

413
00:18:43,466 --> 00:18:44,666
I cried because of that too.

414
00:18:45,426 --> 00:18:46,105
I tried to run away as well.

415
00:18:46,265 --> 00:18:47,745
I even thought about giving up.

416
00:18:48,745 --> 00:18:49,505
But I also want

417
00:18:49,545 --> 00:18:50,305
to prove to him

418
00:18:50,426 --> 00:18:51,426
that I can do this.

419
00:18:52,626 --> 00:18:53,186
Dad.

420
00:18:54,186 --> 00:18:54,906
Don't worry.

