425
00:19:05,186 --> 00:19:06,305
My daughter is unlike me.

426
00:19:06,666 --> 00:19:07,545
My daughter is way stronger

427
00:19:07,706 --> 00:19:08,825
than me.

428
00:19:09,626 --> 00:19:10,426
I know it now.

429
00:19:13,466 --> 00:19:14,146
So...

