435
00:19:24,785 --> 00:19:25,265
It's fine.

436
00:19:25,305 --> 00:19:26,025
You can use it however much you want.

437
00:19:26,226 --> 00:19:26,706
I'll buy you new ones

438
00:19:26,745 --> 00:19:27,545
when you finish this.

439
00:19:28,505 --> 00:19:29,226
Thanks, Dad.

440
00:19:30,226 --> 00:19:31,386
You're welcome.

