00:20:01,505 --> 00:20:02,065
No, thanks.

447
00:20:03,345 --> 00:20:04,105
Not bad.

448
00:20:04,265 --> 00:20:05,585
You're quite self-conscious.

449
00:20:06,866 --> 00:20:08,345
It was just a test.

450
00:20:18,745 --> 00:20:19,265
How did it go?

451
00:20:20,146 --> 00:20:21,186
Did you talk to your dad?

452
00:20:21,785 --> 00:20:23,146
We've reconciled.

453
00:20:25,946 --> 00:20:27,345
You owe me big time,

454
00:20:27,585 --> 00:20:28,186
but it's all right.

